WEBVTT



00:00:10.465 --> 00:00:12.665
Paradorn.

00:00:12.745 --> 00:00:14.945
Paradorn.

00:00:15.025 --> 00:00:16.985
Paradorn.

00:00:18.585 --> 00:00:22.625
They say power changes people.

00:00:23.385 --> 00:00:27.025
