of decentralizing power to class reps.

00:07:33.745 --> 00:07:36.865
If we can push this
as our flagship policy,

00:07:36.945 --> 00:07:39.305
we'll gain more support from voters.

00:07:40.385 --> 00:07:42.145
As for Nanno,

00:07:42.985 --> 00:07:46.865
