00:14:23.865 --> 00:14:24.745
Hey!

00:14:32.585 --> 00:14:33.825
Shit.

00:14:33.905 --> 00:14:35.185
Oh.

00:14:35.865 --> 00:14:36.825
Hey.

00:14:36.905 --> 00:14:39.105
