00:15:04.665 --> 00:15:06.745
THE REAL HERO

00:15:06.825 --> 00:15:08.945
I'LL VOTE FOR HIM

00:15:09.025 --> 00:15:09.945
NO NEED FOR AN ELECTION. CROWN HIM.

