00:17:43.385 --> 00:17:45.145
Damn. I might have already won.

00:17:45.225 --> 00:17:46.385
Damn it.

00:17:46.465 --> 00:17:47.465
Damn.

00:17:47.545 --> 00:17:48.545
Damn you.

00:17:49.065 --> 00:17:51.665
You're really working hard
