00:23:29.705 --> 00:23:30.745
Please answer, sir.

00:23:30.825 --> 00:23:32.065
He's so fake.

00:23:32.145 --> 00:23:33.465
I shouldn't have believed him.

00:23:33.545 --> 00:23:35.505
I'm not voting for you anymore.

00:23:35.585 --> 00:23:36.945
-Yeah, me too.
-You asshole.

00:23:37.545 --> 00:23:40.105
That's not what happened.
Please listen to me.

00:23:40.185 --> 00:23:43.465
Hey, I did my best. I took responsibility.

00:23:43.545 --> 00:23:45.705
Please… I already took responsibility.

00:23:45.785 --> 00:23:46.985
Hey, listen to me.

00:23:47.065 --> 00:23:49.345
I already took responsibility.

00:23:49.425 --> 00:23:52.425
-Sir, answer us.
-What really happened?

00:23:52.505 --> 00:23:55.985
-That's enough. Excuse us.
-Answer us, sir.

00:23:56.065 --> 00:23:58.865
-Excuse us.
-Hey!

00:24:19.065 --> 00:24:20.945
Think again.

00:24:53.185 --> 00:24:54.465
Hey, hurry up.

00:24:54.545 --> 00:24:56.905
Take these three boxes out
and replace them.

00:25:16.985 --> 00:25:20.265
Hello, New.
Call everyone for an urgent meeting.

00:25:21.425 --> 00:25:26.665
I want us to start working on
the smart crosswalk project immediately.

00:25:38.945 --> 00:25:40.865
We finally won, Paradorn.

00:25:40.945 --> 00:25:42.265
Damn, this is amazing.

00:25:43.145 --> 00:25:44.705
I've been waiting for this day.

00:25:45.505 --> 00:25:47.505
ANNUAL POLICY: SMART CROSSWALK PROJECT

00:25:48.185 --> 00:25:49.625
Right, Paradorn?

00:25:51.465 --> 00:25:52.465
Paradorn.

00:25:57.625 --> 00:25:58.625
Hey, Paradorn.

00:26:50.025 --> 00:26:51.985
Are you okay?

00:27:06.425 --> 00:27:07.425
Nanno!

00:27:15.585 --> 00:27:16.585
Nanno!

00:27:19.825 --> 00:27:22.945
Tell me the truth. Is what I saw real?

00:27:24.945 --> 00:27:26.705
You don't have to believe it.

00:27:29.225 --> 00:27:32.385
Then delete that damn clip
right here in front of me.

00:27:34.825 --> 00:27:36.985
I said there's no copy.

00:27:37.065 --> 00:27:39.665
-So then there's no copy.
-You think I'm stupid?

00:27:40.865 --> 00:27:42.825
I don't need a copy.

00:27:51.185 --> 00:27:52.985
Because your wrongdoing

00:27:54.625 --> 00:27:55.785
goes far beyond that.

00:27:55.865 --> 00:27:58.585
Hey. I almost really got hit
by the car earlier.

00:27:58.665 --> 00:28:00.625
You should pay me more.

00:28:00.705 --> 00:28:02.585
We agreed on the price.
That's all you get.

00:28:02.665 --> 00:28:04.185
Why are you asking for more now?

00:28:04.265 --> 00:28:07.145
That accident where you became a hero

00:28:08.225 --> 00:28:10.745
was your doing too, wasn't it?

00:28:14.305 --> 00:28:16.065
Like I said,

00:28:16.145 --> 00:28:21.665
people keep making
the same stupid mistakes until they die.

00:29:16.225 --> 00:29:17.825
Some people,

00:29:18.345 --> 00:29:20.345
even when they stand in the light,

00:29:20.865 --> 00:29:22.905
let darkness consume them.

00:29:27.065 --> 00:29:28.785
But others,

00:29:29.345 --> 00:29:31.185
even when surrounded by darkness,

00:29:32.225 --> 00:29:35.465
refuse to let
their inner light be extinguished.

00:29:48.265 --> 00:29:49.385
Hey!

00:29:54.945 --> 00:29:56.065
Nanno.

00:30:04.025 --> 00:30:05.465
How did you get here?

00:30:08.745 --> 00:30:10.425
Shouldn't I be the one asking you?

00:32:43.345 --> 00:32:45.465
Honestly, I feel happier right now

00:32:45.545 --> 00:32:48.145
than I did
when I was appointed as a minister.

00:32:48.665 --> 00:32:50.385
As everyone knows,

00:32:50.465 --> 00:32:53.345
I first ran for election at this school.

00:32:54.025 --> 00:32:55.225
But it's more than that.

00:32:55.745 --> 00:33:01.185
Everything that made me
who I am today started here.

00:33:01.265 --> 00:33:03.465
HOMECOMING DAY
OUTSTANDING ALUMNUS

00:33:42.745 --> 00:33:44.985
A world that has been reset…

00:33:45.905 --> 00:33:50.785
I hope
there are still some good people left.

00:33:54.665 --> 00:33:58.265
See you again next semester, everyone.

00:36:02.265 --> 00:36:07.265
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon